Pull it together.

34:00.603 --> 34:03.084
Come on, Leslie. Leslie.

34:08.959 --> 34:11.571
It's just...

34:11.614 --> 34:13.486
It's been a really long road.

34:13.529 --> 34:17.577
- Yeah, okay. Okay, okay.
You're okay. Just breathe.

34:21.320 --> 34:23.409
- So listen, Leslie,

34:23.452 --> 34:27.239
I'm gonna take
these women down.

34:27.282 --> 34:29.589
- Yes. Yes!

34:31.199 --> 34:34.246
- Yeah, but I'm gonna need
your help, all right?

34:42.036 --> 34:45.126
What's in it for me?

34:45.170 --> 34:47.041
- Civic pride.

34:47.085 --> 34:49.435
- I was thinking more money.

34:49.478 --> 34:51.437
- Yeah, okay.

34:51.480 --> 34:53.178
Or I just arrest you.

34:55.484 --> 34:57.269
Yeah, right.
For what?

34:57.312 --> 34:59.097
- Oh, Leslie, you're trying to
tell me there's a store manager

34:59.140 --> 35:01.142
that doesn't know exactly
what's going in and out

35:01.186 --> 35:03.013
of his own safe?

35:05.059 --> 35:07.583
How much did they pay you
to look the other way?

35:10.195 --> 35:13.285
- I accept your terms.
- I thought you might.

35:17.158 --> 35:20.640
- Okay, I made
all your favorites...

35:20.683 --> 35:24.731
roast chicken,
potato casserole, apple pie.

35:24.774 --> 35:27.777
- It's 9:00 a.m.

35:27.821 --> 35:31.041
- I know, but I just thought,
you know...

35:31.085 --> 35:33.131
comfort food.

35:38.136 --> 35:40.312
I'm just gonna put it here.

35:41.748 --> 35:45.012
Did you see
what the kids made?

35:45.055 --> 35:46.666
They really wanted
to stay home from school,

35:46.709 --> 35:48.189
but I made them go.

35:48.233 --> 35:50.365
- What happened
to the stop sign?

35:51.584 --> 35:53.194
- I don't know.

35:53.238 --> 35:56.110
Probably some kid took it.

35:56.154 --> 36:00.767
- I've seen, like, five cars
just blow through it.

36:02.595 --> 36:04.814
Somebody's going to get hurt.

36:09.254 --> 36:11.560
- Dean, I--

36:17.436 --> 36:18.698
Do you want me
to turn on the TV?

36:18.741 --> 36:20.613
- Not right now.
- Okay.

36:20.656 --> 36:23.093
Let me know.
- Mm-hmm.

36:26.271 --> 36:28.229
- All right, all right,
all right, check this out.

36:28.273 --> 36:30.536
I've got an H
and an S here.

36:30.579 --> 36:32.233
Look at that.
- It looks more like an 8.

36:32.277 --> 36:33.669
- Yeah, 'cause the batter
ran over a little.

36:33.713 --> 36:35.628
So that's why--
- That looks like a snowman.

36:35.671 --> 36:37.543
- It kind
of looks like Grandma.

36:37.586 --> 36:39.414
- What?

36:39.458 --> 36:41.329
- Oh, that is your mother.

36:41.373 --> 36:43.853
- Ew, in that sundress,
right?

36:43.897 --> 36:46.552
- For sure.

36:46.595 --> 36:48.336
- You all better stop talking
about my mama.

36:48.380 --> 36:50.512
All right, fine. You know what?
I'm going to eat these.

36:50.556 --> 36:53.733
I'm gonna call her and tell her
you said that, Lil' Money.

36:55.213 --> 36:57.258
- Maybe
we can play cards later.

37:03.917 --> 37:06.441
- Thank you.

37:06.485 --> 37:07.877
- I did it for them.

37:14.188 --> 37:16.669
- Hi!
- Hi.

37:16.712 --> 37:18.845
- Come on, come on, come on,
come on, come on, come on!

37:18.888 --> 37:21.326
- What?
- I just--I've been--

37:21.369 --> 37:23.284
I've been thinking
a lot about this,

37:23.328 --> 37:26.722
and we should go skydiving.

37:26.766 --> 37:28.811
- Like, jump out of a plane?

37:28.855 --> 37:30.552
- No, like to the mall.

37:30.596 --> 37:32.598
You know they got those
big wind tube-y things,

37:32.641 --> 37:34.469
and you can just fly.

37:34.513 --> 37:36.384
- I have a secret.

37:36.428 --> 37:38.778
- What is it?
- I'm not supposed to tell.

37:38.821 --> 37:40.519
- Dude, come on.
Well, now you have to tell me.

37:40.562 --> 37:43.478
What is it?
- Nancy's pregs.

37:45.567 --> 37:46.699
- Wow.

37:46.742 --> 37:48.831
- She just found out
this morning.

37:50.572 --> 37:52.357
- Wow.

37:52.400 --> 37:53.880
- She was crying
and then laughing,

37:53.923 --> 37:55.708
and then she barfed
all over the counter.

37:55.751 --> 37:58.885
-  Wow!

38:00.365 --> 38:01.540
- It's good, right?

38:01.583 --> 38:03.803
They've been trying
a long time.

38:03.846 --> 38:06.240
- I mean...

38:06.284 --> 38:07.502
Wow.

38:07.546 --> 38:10.462
- You keep saying that.

38:10.505 --> 38:12.812
- Yeah, I'm just, uh...

38:12.855 --> 38:16.337
I'm just really happy
for them.

38:16.381 --> 38:18.644
- So...

38:18.687 --> 38:20.341
Do you want to go?

38:20.385 --> 38:23.344
- Where?
- To the mall. Skydiving.

38:23.388 --> 38:24.693
- To the mall!
- To the mall!

38:24.737 --> 38:27.696
- Skydiving!

38:29.655 --> 38:32.484
- Go away. I said I don't want
to talk to you.

38:32.527 --> 38:33.833
I'm going to call the cops.

38:33.876 --> 38:35.878
- Ask for my boy, Jimmy.

38:35.922 --> 38:37.358
He's the one investigating

38:37.402 --> 38:39.491
those bitches
you're in bed with.

38:39.534 --> 38:41.841
- How do you know that?

38:41.884 --> 38:44.234
- I'm his key witness.

38:46.585 --> 38:49.370
- Well, I don't know
anything, so...

38:49.414 --> 38:51.285
- Okay.

38:51.329 --> 38:53.243
- I mean, they kept me
out of it. I--

38:53.287 --> 38:56.464
- Well, good. I mean, 'cause
they're in real big trouble.

38:56.508 --> 38:58.901
- Like jail or--

39:00.729 --> 39:02.905
I'm just--

39:05.908 --> 39:07.954
- Did you take money
from them?

39:07.997 --> 39:10.260
- No.

39:12.872 --> 39:14.395
- Well, then you're cool.

39:18.051 --> 39:21.315
- I took a little--
I took a little money.

39:25.537 --> 39:27.626
- How much?

39:27.669 --> 39:29.497
- It wasn't not a lot.

39:29.541 --> 39:31.238
- Oh, Mary Pat.

39:31.281 --> 39:33.545
- But I have kids.
Leslie, I--

39:35.460 --> 39:37.679
I wish I could help you.
I do, uh--

39:37.723 --> 39:39.420
- Please. No, please don't
tell them about me.

39:39.464 --> 39:42.902
- I am going
to be under oath.

39:42.945 --> 39:46.427
You know, I got to tell
the truth, so help me God.

39:46.471 --> 39:48.690
- I can't go away
for this, Leslie.

39:48.734 --> 39:50.736
Please. I ca--
I mean, I ca--Please.

39:50.779 --> 39:52.433
Can you just leave me
out of it, and then--

39:52.477 --> 39:54.435
and then I can stay with--
with my boys?

39:54.479 --> 39:56.959
Please.
Please, Leslie, please.

39:57.003 --> 39:58.744
Please, please.

39:58.787 --> 40:01.442
- Okay, okay.

40:01.486 --> 40:03.792
- Okay.

40:03.836 --> 40:05.403
- Okay.

40:05.446 --> 40:07.883
-  Thank you.
Thank you.

40:13.715 --> 40:15.587
- What are you doing?

40:15.630 --> 40:18.590
- Well, a husband can't testify
against his wife.

40:21.506 --> 40:24.509
- Hey, don't forget
to order for everybody.

40:24.552 --> 40:26.772
- Oh, God.
K-Bear's in it for himself.

40:26.815 --> 40:28.774
- Order for your sisters!

40:28.817 --> 40:32.342
- Yeah,
and your favorite auntie!

40:32.386 --> 40:35.476
- Uh-oh.
- Uh-uh.

40:35.520 --> 40:36.999
- Really?

40:37.043 --> 40:39.611
- That's all the money.
- I gave him ten bucks.

40:39.654 --> 40:42.614
- Yo, what about my frog pop?
We had a deal!

40:44.572 --> 40:46.444
- That grifter got four scoops.

40:46.487 --> 40:48.620
- I'm telling you.
That kid's shady as hell.

40:48.663 --> 40:51.840
- We should go.

40:51.884 --> 40:54.843
- Nah, let the kid eat.

40:54.887 --> 40:56.845
What's up? You miss me?

40:58.586 --> 41:00.501
- No.

41:02.503 --> 41:05.375
- So crazy thing--
turns out...

41:05.419 --> 41:07.465
we got a mutual friend.

41:07.508 --> 41:08.814
That's you're homey, right?

41:08.857 --> 41:10.511
- No, he's not my homey.

41:10.555 --> 41:11.686
I don't know
why everybody keeps--

41:11.730 --> 41:13.993
- He's talking
to the Feds now...

41:14.036 --> 41:16.517
which could be bad
for all of us.

41:16.561 --> 41:18.998
So, yeah, I'm gonna need you
to take care of him.

41:20.869 --> 41:23.002
- That's insane.

41:23.045 --> 41:25.657
- Is it? Why?

41:25.700 --> 41:28.877
- Because we don't do that.
- Yeah, that's not what we do.

41:28.921 --> 41:30.662
- Besides,
don't you have anyone

41:30.705 --> 41:32.838
who's a little
more experienced

41:32.881 --> 41:34.840
in that particular arena?

41:34.883 --> 41:38.060
- Sure, but it ain't on him.
It's on you.

41:38.104 --> 41:40.759
- Daddy! You said five minutes.
- What's up, pop?

41:40.802 --> 41:42.587
You're right, no.
I did, I did.

41:42.630 --> 41:45.024
Hey, what's that thing I always
tell you when you make

41:45.067 --> 41:46.721
a big old mess?

41:46.765 --> 41:48.636
- That I got to clean it up.

41:48.680 --> 41:51.160
- That you got to clean it up.

41:53.728 --> 41:56.818
All right, come on.
No more grown-up talk.

41:56.862 --> 41:58.559
That's for you.

42:05.218 --> 42:07.568
- What is it?

42:07.612 --> 42:09.570
- What is it, Beth?
